parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motorized seat belt can cause the seat belt to become stuck or inoperable, which can lead to accidents or injuries due to the lack of proper restraint.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract or move along the track
the seat belt is stuck in one position
the seat belt motor still runs but the belt does not move
the track cable has fallen out of its housing
the seat belt is loose or does not engage properly
the seat belt light is constantly on.
